  "title": "Junior Sales & Marketing Executive (Career Development | Training Provided)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Sales & Marketing Executive (Career Development | Training Provided)</strong></h3><p>This role is ideal for individuals who are serious about <strong>building a long-term career</strong> in sales, marketing, and campaign execution. You’ll gain hands-on experience, structured training, and mentorship while working on real client campaigns.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong><br />📌 Support the execution of sales and marketing campaigns<br />💬 Engage customers professionally and communicate brand messages clearly<br />📊 Track performance, generate leads, and contribute to campaign results<br />🤝 Work closely with team leaders to improve campaign effectiveness<br />📈 Continuously develop skills in sales, communication, and teamwork</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get</strong><br />🎓 Structured training with clear skill progression<br />👔 Mentorship from experienced leaders<br />🏢 Exposure to real-world sales and marketing campaigns<br />✈️ Opportunities to travel for campaigns<br />🚀 Clear career path into senior or leadership roles<br />💰 Performance-based earnings</p><p><strong>Who This Role Is For</strong><br />✔ Individuals motivated to grow professionally<br />✔ Candidates with strong communication skills and a learning mindset<br />✔ Team players who value feedback and improvement<br />✔ No prior experience required — full training provided</p><p></p>",
